&lt;p&gt;Tika Core API identifying the content of a txt file re-named with .csv extension as text/csv instead of text/plain&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16782213" author="tallison@mitre.org" created="Fri, 1 Mar 2019 23:49:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We just added a csv detector. Up until last week, we did detection of csv only by filename. If you can grab a nightly build or share your file, it&#8217;d be interesting to see if the new detector works on your file.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
