                            <comment id="16786555" author="dagnelies" created="Thu, 7 Mar 2019 09:32:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looking at the file content, it does a bit look like a CSV file... Just with a txt extension.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;That said, IMHO, I think too it would definitely make sense to give priority to the file extension rather than content type detection.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
