                            <comment id="16787325" author="tallison@mitre.org" created="Thu, 7 Mar 2019 23:36:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry.  Right. The parser is where the byte-based detection happens. I couldn&#8217;t easily figure out how to do detection after MimeTypes without putting it in the Parser.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
